---
source: crates/runtime/tests/metadata/mod.rs
expression: explain_met_all_location_filtered
---
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: met_all.id ASC NULLS LAST, met_all.location ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |   Filter: met_all.location = Utf8("s3://spiceai-public-datasets/hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet")                                                                                                         |
|               |     TableScan: met_all projection=[id, value, year, month, day, last_modified, location, size], partial_filters=[met_all.location = Utf8("s3://spiceai-public-datasets/hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet")] |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [id@0 ASC NULLS LAST, location@6 ASC NULLS LAST]                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |   SortExec: expr=[id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |     FilterExec: location@6 = s3://spiceai-public-datasets/hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet                                                                                                                 |
|               |       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |           DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet]]}, projection=[id, value, year, month, day, last_modified, location, size], file_type=parquet                          |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
